killing Hae Ra's dad and my dad.

606
00:44:14.700 --> 00:44:15.700
Hi.

607
00:44:16.630 --> 00:44:18.371
Director Han Myung Soo. Nice to meet you.

608
00:44:18.371 --> 00:44:19.641
Nice to meet you.

609
00:44:20.041 --> 00:44:21.470
I didn't know...

610
