Chan Ki was working with such a great boss.

611
00:44:25.180 --> 00:44:27.481
Uncle Myung Soo, thank you.

612
00:44:27.711 --> 00:44:29.410
Hey,

613
00:44:29.410 --> 00:44:31.981
