673
00:47:46.641 --> 00:47:49.450
My name is Koo Jang Bin.

674
00:47:51.550 --> 00:47:52.581
You didn't...

675
00:47:53.380 --> 00:47:55.090
draw this painting?

676
00:47:55.891 --> 00:47:57.191
My grandfather's...

677
00:47:57.191 --> 00:47:59.961
